title: Ex-Genesis CEO Michael Moro to Head Crypto Derivatives Exchange Startup

title: COMP Token Rises by 50% in 4 Days Amid Flurry of Whale Activity on Binance

title: Binance Loses European Banking Partner Paysafe
description: Binance's European banking partner Paysafe Payment Solutions will terminate support for the world’s largest crypto exchange in September.
